            <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value="&#x9;           Files Scheduler&#xa;&#xa;This software allows copying or moving from a source directory to a destination directory.&#xa;You can choose to respect the folder hierarchy of the source directory or create a hierarchy based on year, month and file extension, to note that empty folders will not be moved or copied.&#xa;A check is also carried out on the contents of the files in the destination folder and if a file with the same content is found, the copy or movement of the same is bypassed, instead if a file with the same nomenclature but different in the content is found, it is automatically renamed.&#xa;The log window contains all the operations performed."/>
